OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FMinisters urged to issue   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fcap on Scottish bus fares  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The Scottish government is being urged 
OL,6, to introduce a cap on bus fares.       
OL,8,FMore than 130 bus operators in England 
OL,9,Fhave signed up to limit fares to #2 for
OL,10,Fthe first three months of the year.    
OL,12,FScottish Labour wants Scotland to      
OL,13,Ffollow suit to stop people seeking     
OL,14,Falternative transport.                 
OL,16,FThe Scottish government said its       
OL,17,Fconcessionary bus travel schemes were  
OL,18,Fthe most generous in the UK, with free 
OL,19,Ftravel for under-22s, over-60s, and    
OL,20,Fpeople with disabilities.              
